qu%C3%A2n-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o/poem-dwsKivXoJ5TA_Qil5ceCng">Tòng quân khẩu hào - 從軍口號</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Tr%E1%BB%ABng-Chi/author-V8R7nhhotOVWLkm8vPg4Jg">Tiền Trừng Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-05/poem-FQy6SFlN_wLa8mx_G7hJRw">Trúc chi ca kỳ 05 - 竹枝歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-HbKyCtS3WFreEebdROalkQ">Uông Nguyên Lượng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Xa-c%C3%B4ng-3/poem-3j54QSyfzv_SMaWNYAQ6Fg">Xa công 3 - 車攻 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-tr%E1%BA%A7n/poem--MNivfmhfmKdaENtm576XQ">Xuất trần - 出塵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
